{
  "stem": "24409.9",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, I didn't have to enter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wanted to fly straight over Spain to Portugal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I talked my way out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he let we continue to Portugal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in Portugal, where I arrived, the Portugal authorities said, this visa may not valid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We have to deport you tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We have a plane going-- leaving for Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I faced, now, what has helped me before-- the real thing-- at first I slit my wrist again, but not deep enough to die for me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they brought me to the hospital in Lisbon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the meanwhile, I got-- I got-- I got the permission to stay-- to stay in Portugal for, I think, two months or so.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, the war had really broken out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The war had broken out on the first of September, but there was no fighting except Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the Western Front, on the 10th of May, 19-- 1940, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans invaded Holland and Belgium and France.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now many, many refugees came over to Portugal from France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't wait for these two months to be over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, the situation was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I learned from one of the refugees that you can get a visa to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went, and I got-- I don't think I went myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got it for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got a visa to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, how do you get to Shanghai from Portugal?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I inquire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no ships going to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, first of all, I wanted from Portugal, still to continue the organization of the trips.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe [INAUDIBLE] boat and bring the people who were around Portugal out.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
